Commonly used plugins:
----------------------
    Deployment plugins:
    -------------------
        deployment to container plugin, deploys apps to servers like WebLogic, Jboss, GlassFish
        WebLogin/ WebSphere/ WildFly plugins
        server-specific deployments

    * Most widely used = Deploy to container plugin (high adoption)

    Build Dependency Tools:
    -----------------------
        Maven integration plugin: build java projects using maven

    Notification Plugin:
    --------------------
        Email extension plugin: send customized email notifications (failure/success)

    Slack Integration (vai plugin):
    -------------------------------
        Send build alerts to slack

    Code Quality:
    -------------
        Integrates jenkins with sonarqube for code analysis

    Monitoring & Audit:
    -------------------
        Tracks: who created jobs, who deleted jobs, who modified configs
        Limitation: cannot create restore deleted jobs

    Recovery & History:
    -------------------
        Job configuration history plugin: tracks config changes, can restore deleted jobs

    Build Management:
    -----------------
        next build number plugin: change build numbers manually
        Real use case: After jenkins crash -> new server -> avoid version conflicts

    Backup:
    -------
        ThinBackup plugin: backup jenkins configs and jobs

    UI Enhancement:
    ---------------
        Blue Ocean Plugin: Modern UI for pipelines

    Scheduling:
    -----------
        Schedule Build Plugin: Run job one time at a specific time

    File Transfer:
    --------------
        Publish over SSH plugin: transfer files between servers

    Build Customization:
    --------------------
        Build Name Setter: Customize build names (e.g, dev_1, instead of #1)